{
  "stem": "26728.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was-- he was-- uh, had a real white circle around his mouth, and his hands were shaking, and I-- the guy was just almost beside himself.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was-- by then, I was pretty calm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was very angry, I mean, and just on the edge of a rage, but this guy was in a rage.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when he tried to smoke the cigarette, it was, you know, Jesus, I said, I hope he doesn't-- and some of these guys smoked in the airplane, and I hated-- you're not supposed to do that, you know, because it's a fabric airplane, and with wooden floors, and stuff.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's not too cool to smoke in those damn airplanes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, we get-- we get in the airplane and I'm going to start the engine and there's, you know, there's a guy out there with a fire extinguisher.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, um, before I said to the-- to the, uh, to guy with the fire extinguisher, who happened to be a tanker, this general, or this colonel said to me, you know-- and he was almost talking to himself-- he said, I wonder how many more of these fucking places we're going to find?",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just fired it up and we took off and went back to Frankfurt, and I never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I thought about that a lot, what, you know, what a shock it must've been to him to say something like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- because I felt like screaming, you know, and pounding on something or doing something physical, like I said.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The tendency is-- I don't know if women are like it or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Men tend to want to cause pain and do physical.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
